    <description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/img/roughtrack.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><figure><a class="lightgallery" href="/apps/roughtrack/images/feature_graphic.png" title="" data-thumbnail="/apps/roughtrack/images/feature_graphic.png" data-sub-html="<h2>Now Next Later Roadmap for Small Teams</h2>"><img  loading="lazy" src=https://rustycruiselabs.github.io/apps/roughtrack/images/feature_graphic.png    height="350" width="700"></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Now Next Later Roadmap for Small Teams</figcaption>
    </figure>
<h2 id="overview" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#overview" class="header-mark"></a>Overview</h2><p>RoughTrack is a lightweight, opinionated tool designed to help teams plan and communicate priorities through simple Now-Next-Later roadmaps. It focuses on clarity over complexity, allowing teams to capture what matters most, stay aligned, and share progress effortlessly.</p>
<p>It&rsquo;s not built to be the next Jira or Linear. RoughTrack is a simplified tool for small teams and individuals who just want a straightforward way to prioritize tasks and communicate what’s coming next.</p>]]></description>
